text: Henderson Island may refer to: * Henderson Island (Pitcairn Islands), in the southern Pacific Ocean * Henderson Island (Shackleton Ice Shelf), in Antarctica * Henderson Island (Colorado), located in the South Platte River, US; See John D. Henderson * Henderson Island (Kentucky), located in the Ohio River, US; See List of islands by name (H) * Henderson Islets, south-eastern Australia
title: Henderson Island
